### OCR Image Upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/ocr/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

-- Use your REST client UI to attach the file under field name `image` --

# Example response:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "message": "File uploaded successfully",
#   "filePath": "uploads/ocr/1680606931221_my_image.png",
#   "originalName": "my_image.png",
#   "mimeType": "image/png",
#   "size": 12345
# }
